## Phase 1 - Discovery and Scope Mapping

Date: 2026-03-28
Status: Completed

### Objective
Map current admin/offline order architecture and identify integration points for offline returns without changing code.

### Files Inspected
- src/app/(admin)/admin/orders/actions.ts
- src/app/(admin)/admin/orders/OrderTable.tsx
- src/app/(admin)/admin/orders/page.tsx
- src/app/(tenant-admin)/[tenant]/admin/orders/page.tsx
